page.title: 05Birds and Animals.
page.content: In the nature reserve there are many types of animals and birds .{ {270 different species of birds}have been recorded in the Nature Reserve including Great Crested Grebe,Wrens, Coots, Moorhen, Mute Swans, Reed Warblers, Herons, Gulls, and Wagtails. Kestrels nest in the month of June and the{rarest bird}seen in the reserve was a{Sooty Owl. {The creatures in the reserve} are grass snakes, foxes, rabbits, bats, hares, mice,rats, badgers, marsh frogs, newts and lizards. Some of the creatures on the beach are shrimps, starfish, masked crabs, lugworm, razor shells and ragworms, also there are 14 kinds of grass hopper.{In the {lakes}sticklebacks, snails and large fish are feeding. {*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
